        "title": "AI Prompt Interface",
        "category": "UI Inspiration",
        "visual_html": "<div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden font-sans max-w-full mx-auto\">\n<div class=\"bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200 px-4 py-2 flex items-center gap-3\">\n<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-600\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0zM10 7v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0H7\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n<span class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 text-xs tracking-wide uppercase m-0\">SEO Optimization Prompt</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-4 md:p-8 flex flex-col gap-2 bg-gray-50 items-stretch\">\n<!-- Prompt Box -->\n<!-- Output Preview -->\n<div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-4 relative overflow-hidden w-full\">\n<div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 bg-green-500 text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-lg uppercase tracking-wider shadow-sm m-0\">Output</div>\n<h1 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 pr-10 m-0 leading-tight\">The Most Accurate <span class=\"bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded px-1\">Online Ruler</span> for Your Device</h1>\n<p class=\"text-xs text-gray-600 mb-2 leading-relaxed m-0\">\n                Need to measure something but don't have a physical tape measure? Our <span class=\"bg-yellow-100 border-b-2 border-yellow-300 font-medium px-1\">screen ruler online</span> is perfectly calibrated. Whether you need a <span class=\"bg-yellow-100 border-b-2 border-yellow-300 font-medium px-1\">pixel ruler online</span> for web design or just want to <span class=\"bg-yellow-100 border-b-2 border-yellow-300 font-medium px-1\">measure online ruler</span> objects quickly, this tool works directly in your browser.\n            </p>\n<h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 mt-2 m-0\">Perfect <span class=\"bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded px-1\">Online Ruler for Mobile</span></h2>\n<p class=\"text-xs text-gray-600 mb-0 leading-relaxed m-0\">\n                Unlike older tools, this <span class=\"bg-yellow-100 border-b-2 border-yellow-300 font-medium px-1\">ruler online</span> adapts to your exact screen size...\n            </p>\n<div class=\"mt-3 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100 flex items-center justify-between\">\n<div class=\"text-[10px] text-gray-400 font-mono m-0\">&lt;h1&gt;, &lt;h2&gt;, meta tags optimized</div>\n<div class=\"text-[10px] text-green-600 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-bold shadow-sm m-0 whitespace-nowrap\">SEO Score: 98/100</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
        "metadata_html": "<div class=\"mb-4\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">Why I saved this:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>Keyword chip design</li><li>Clear conversational structure</li><li>Subtle border styling</li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-6\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">What I can learn:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>Structuring LLM outputs visually</li><li>Tag system UI patterns</li></ul>\n</div>\n<!-- RESTORED: SOURCE METADATA -->\n<div class=\"transparent p-4 rounded border border-white/20 text-sm mt-4 hidden\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-y-2 gap-x-4\">\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Creator:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Tejas Jaware</div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Source:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-[var(--text-primary)]\"><a class=\"underline font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] hover:text-indigo-500\" href=\"paper_micro_tool.html\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">AI Micro-Tools Guide</a></div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Rights:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-gray-500 text-xs italic leading-tight mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Belongs to original creator. Saved for inspiration.</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
