        "id": "visual_16",
        "title": "CLI / Terminal Mockup",
        "category": "My Experiments",
        "visual_html": "<div class=\"border-2 border-black rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] w-full max-w-full mx-auto\">\n<div class=\"bg-purple-100 border-b-2 border-black px-4 py-1.5 flex items-center space-x-2\">\n<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-purple-700\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n<span class=\"font-bold text-xs tracking-wide text-purple-900\">FAQ SECTION &amp; STRUCTURED DATA</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-4 bg-white space-y-1.5\">\n<!-- Data Sources -->\n<div class=\"flex justify-center space-x-6\">\n<div class=\"border-2 border-black rounded-lg bg-orange-50 p-3 shadow-[2px_2px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] w-40 text-center\">\n<div class=\"font-bold text-orange-600 text-xs mb-1\">Ahrefs</div>\n<div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Keyword Questions</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"border-2 border-black rounded-lg bg-blue-50 p-3 shadow-[2px_2px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] w-40 text-center\">\n<div class=\"font-bold text-blue-600 text-xs mb-1\">Google PAA</div>\n<div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">\"People Also Ask\"</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-center text-gray-400\">\n<svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-2\">\n<!-- FAQ Accordion -->\n<div class=\"border-2 border-black rounded-lg p-4 shadow-[3px_3px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] bg-white\">\n<div class=\"text-xs font-bold border-b border-gray-200 pb-2 mb-1.5\">Website Display</div>\n<div class=\"space-y-2\">\n<div class=\"border border-gray-200 rounded p-2 flex justify-between items-center bg-gray-50\">\n<span class=\"text-xs font-bold\">What is this tool?</span>\n<span>+</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"border border-gray-200 rounded p-2 flex justify-between items-center bg-gray-50\">\n<span class=\"text-xs font-bold\">How does it work?</span>\n<span>+</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"border border-gray-200 rounded p-2 flex justify-between items-center bg-gray-50\">\n<span class=\"text-xs font-bold\">Is it free?</span>\n<span>+</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- JSON-LD -->\n<div class=\"border-2 border-black rounded-lg p-4 shadow-[3px_3px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] bg-[#1e1e1e]\">\n<div class=\"text-xs font-bold border-b border-gray-700 pb-2 mb-1.5 text-white\">JSON-LD Schema (Hidden)</div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-xs text-[#d4d4d4] leading-tight space-y-1\">\n<div>&lt;<span class=\"text-[#569cd6]\">script</span> <span class=\"text-[#9cdcfe]\">type</span>=<span class=\"text-[#ce9178]\">\"application/ld+json\"</span>&gt;</div>\n<div class=\"pl-2\">{</div>\n<div class=\"pl-4\">\"<span class=\"text-[#9cdcfe]\">@context</span>\": \"<span class=\"text-[#ce9178]\">https://schema.org</span>\",</div>\n<div class=\"pl-4\">\"<span class=\"text-[#9cdcfe]\">@type</span>\": \"<span class=\"text-[#ce9178]\">FAQPage</span>\",</div>\n<div class=\"pl-4\">\"<span class=\"text-[#9cdcfe]\">mainEntity</span>\": [{</div>\n<div class=\"pl-6\">\"<span class=\"text-[#9cdcfe]\">@type</span>\": \"<span class=\"text-[#ce9178]\">Question</span>\",</div>\n<div class=\"pl-6\">\"<span class=\"text-[#9cdcfe]\">name</span>\": \"<span class=\"text-[#ce9178]\">What is this tool?</span>\",</div>\n<div class=\"pl-6\">...</div>\n<div class=\"pl-4\">}]</div>\n<div class=\"pl-2\">}</div>\n<div>&lt;/<span class=\"text-[#569cd6]\">script</span>&gt;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded p-3 text-center text-xs font-bold text-green-800\">\n            Improves chances of appearing in Google Rich Snippets!\n        </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
        "metadata_html": "<div class=\"mb-4\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">Why I saved this:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>High contrast monospaced typography</li><li>Realistic macOS traffic lights</li><li>Clean shadow elevation</li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-6\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">What I can learn:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>How to build realistic code snippets</li><li>Simulating CLI outputs in HTML</li></ul>\n</div>\n<!-- RESTORED: SOURCE METADATA -->\n<div class=\"transparent p-4 rounded border border-white/20 text-sm mt-4 hidden\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-y-2 gap-x-4\">\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Creator:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Tejas Jaware</div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Source:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-[var(--text-primary)]\"><a class=\"underline font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] hover:text-indigo-500\" href=\"paper_micro_tool.html\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">AI Micro-Tools Guide</a></div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Rights:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-gray-500 text-xs italic leading-tight mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Belongs to original creator. Saved for inspiration.</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
