        "metadata_html": "<div class=\"mb-4\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">Why I saved this:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>High contrast monospaced typography</li><li>Realistic macOS traffic lights</li><li>Clean shadow elevation</li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-6\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">What I can learn:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>How to build realistic code snippets</li><li>Simulating CLI outputs in HTML</li></ul>\n</div>\n<!-- RESTORED: SOURCE METADATA -->\n<div class=\"transparent p-4 rounded border border-white/20 text-sm mt-4 hidden\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-y-2 gap-x-4\">\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Creator:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Tejas Jaware</div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Source:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-[var(--text-primary)]\"><a class=\"underline font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] hover:text-indigo-500\" href=\"paper_micro_tool.html\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">AI Micro-Tools Guide</a></div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Rights:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-gray-500 text-xs italic leading-tight mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Belongs to original creator. Saved for inspiration.</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
