        "visual_html": "<div class=\"border-2 border-black rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] w-full max-w-full mx-auto\">\n<div class=\"bg-gray-100 border-b-2 border-black px-4 py-1.5 flex items-center space-x-2\">\n<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-gray-700\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n<span class=\"font-bold text-xs tracking-wide\">DNS CONFIGURATION: CLOUDFLARE + REGISTRAR</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-4 bg-white space-y-1.5\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2 items-stretch\">\n<!-- Cloudflare Dashboard -->\n<div class=\"flex-1 border-2 border-black rounded-lg bg-white shadow-[3px_3px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] p-4 relative\">\n<div class=\"text-[#f38020] font-bold text-xs mb-1.5 flex items-center border-b border-gray-200 pb-2\">\n<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 mr-1\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M19.4 9.6a7.5 7.5 0 00-14.8-1.4 5.5 5.5 0 101.4 10.8h12a4.5 4.5 0 100-9z\"></path></svg>\n                    Cloudflare Dashboard\n                </div>\n<div class=\"space-y-1.5 text-xs\">\n<div>\n<span class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs uppercase\">Add Domain</span>\n<div class=\"font-bold\">realonlineruler.com</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<span class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs uppercase\">Plan</span>\n<div class=\"font-bold\">Free</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded p-2 font-mono text-xs\">\n                        A record @ \u2192 8.8.8.8\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded p-2\">\n<span class=\"text-blue-800 text-xs font-bold uppercase block mb-1\">Assigned Nameservers:</span>\n<div class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs text-blue-900\">ns1.cloudflare.com</div>\n<div class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs text-blue-900\">ns2.cloudflare.com</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Arrow -->\n<div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400\">\n<svg class=\"w-8 h-8\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n</div>\n<!-- Registrar Panel -->\n<div class=\"flex-1 border-2 border-black rounded-lg bg-white shadow-[3px_3px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] p-4\">\n<div class=\"font-bold text-xs mb-1.5 text-gray-800 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2\">\n                    Registrar Domain Panel\n                </div>\n<div class=\"space-y-2 text-xs\">\n<div>\n<span class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs uppercase\">Manage Domain</span>\n<div class=\"font-bold\">realonlineruler.com</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"space-y-2\">\n<label class=\"text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase\">Update Name Servers:</label>\n<input class=\"w-full border-2 border-gray-300 rounded px-2 py-1.5 font-mono text-xs bg-gray-50\" readonly=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"ns1.cloudflare.com\"/>\n<input class=\"w-full border-2 border-gray-300 rounded px-2 py-1.5 font-mono text-xs bg-gray-50\" readonly=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"ns2.cloudflare.com\"/>\n</div>\n<button class=\"w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 rounded border-2 border-blue-800 shadow-[2px_2px_0px_0px_rgba(30,58,138,1)] transition-transform active:translate-y-0.5 active:shadow-none\">\n                        Update Nameservers\n                    </button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Custom Domain Routing -->\n<div class=\"bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between text-xs\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-purple-800 font-medium\">\n<span class=\"bg-purple-200 px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs font-bold\">Then</span>\n<span>Workers &amp; Pages \u2192 Project \u2192 Custom Domain</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 font-mono font-bold mt-2 sm:mt-0 bg-white border border-purple-200 px-3 py-1.5 rounded\">\n                realonlineruler.com <span class=\"text-purple-400 mx-1\">+</span> www \u2192 <span class=\"text-green-600 ml-1\">Activate</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
        "metadata_html": "<div class=\"mb-4\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">Why I saved this:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>High contrast primary colors</li><li>Crisp 1px solid borders</li><li>Clear geometric structure</li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-6\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">What I can learn:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>Using color to signify step state</li><li>Connecting logical flows clearly</li></ul>\n</div>\n<!-- RESTORED: SOURCE METADATA -->\n<div class=\"transparent p-4 rounded border border-white/20 text-sm mt-4 hidden\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-y-2 gap-x-4\">\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Creator:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Tejas Jaware</div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Source:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-[var(--text-primary)]\"><a class=\"underline font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] hover:text-indigo-500\" href=\"paper_micro_tool.html\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">AI Micro-Tools Guide</a></div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Rights:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-gray-500 text-xs italic leading-tight mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Belongs to original creator. Saved for inspiration.</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
