        "visual_html": "<div class=\"border-2 border-black rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] w-full max-w-full mx-auto\">\n<div class=\"bg-red-100 border-b-2 border-black px-4 py-1.5 flex items-center space-x-2\">\n<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-red-700\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n<span class=\"font-bold text-xs tracking-wide text-red-900\">FIX DUPLICATE CONTENT: NO-INDEX SUBDOMAIN</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-4 space-y-1.5 bg-white\">\n<div class=\"border-2 border-black rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-[#1e1e1e] shadow-[3px_3px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]\">\n<div class=\"bg-[#2d2d2d] border-b border-[#404040] px-3 py-2 flex items-center text-xs text-gray-300 font-mono\">\n<svg class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-gray-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V9.414a1 1 0 00-.293-.707l-5.414-5.414A1 1 0 0012.586 3H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n                public/_headers\n            </div>\n<div class=\"p-4 font-mono text-xs\">\n<div class=\"text-[#ce9178]\">https://:real-online-ruler.pages.dev/*</div>\n<div class=\"text-[#9cdcfe] pl-4\">X-Robots-Tag<span class=\"text-[#d4d4d4]\">:</span> <span class=\"text-[#b5cea8]\">noindex</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-center text-xs font-mono bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200\">\n<span class=\"text-gray-500 mr-2\">After adding, run:</span>\n<span class=\"font-bold bg-black text-white px-2 py-1 rounded\">$ npm run deploy</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"space-y-1.5 border-t-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 pt-5\">\n<div class=\"font-bold text-xs text-gray-800 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Result:</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between bg-red-50 border border-red-200 p-3 rounded-lg\">\n<div class=\"font-mono text-xs font-bold text-gray-700\">[pages.dev]</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\">\n<span class=\"border-2 border-red-500 text-red-600 font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs transform -rotate-2\">NOINDEX</span>\n<span class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">(Google ignores)</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between bg-green-50 border border-green-200 p-3 rounded-lg\">\n<div class=\"font-mono text-xs font-bold text-gray-700\">[realonlineruler.com]</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\">\n<span class=\"border-2 border-green-500 text-green-600 font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs transform rotate-2\">INDEX</span>\n<span class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">(Google ranks)</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
        "metadata_html": "<div class=\"mb-4\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">Why I saved this:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>High contrast monospaced typography</li><li>Realistic macOS traffic lights</li><li>Clean shadow elevation</li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-6\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">What I can learn:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>How to build realistic code snippets</li><li>Simulating CLI outputs in HTML</li></ul>\n</div>\n<!-- RESTORED: SOURCE METADATA -->\n<div class=\"transparent p-4 rounded border border-white/20 text-sm mt-4 hidden\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-y-2 gap-x-4\">\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Creator:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Tejas Jaware</div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Source:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-[var(--text-primary)]\"><a class=\"underline font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] hover:text-indigo-500\" href=\"paper_micro_tool.html\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">AI Micro-Tools Guide</a></div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Rights:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-gray-500 text-xs italic leading-tight mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Belongs to original creator. Saved for inspiration.</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
