        "visual_html": "<div class=\"border-2 border-black rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] w-full max-w-full mx-auto\">\n<div class=\"bg-yellow-100 border-b-2 border-black px-4 py-1.5 flex items-center space-x-2\">\n<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-yellow-700\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n<span class=\"font-bold text-xs tracking-wide text-yellow-900\">GOOGLE ANALYTICS SETUP</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-4 space-y-1.5 bg-white\">\n<!-- Checklist -->\n<div class=\"space-y-1.5\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3 text-xs\">\n<div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-yellow-200 text-yellow-800 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs shrink-0 mt-0.5\">1</div>\n<div>Go to <span class=\"font-mono bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded\">analytics.google.com</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3 text-xs\">\n<div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-yellow-200 text-yellow-800 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs shrink-0 mt-0.5\">2</div>\n<div>Create account \u2192 Web stream \u2192 enter domain</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3 text-xs\">\n<div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-yellow-200 text-yellow-800 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs shrink-0 mt-0.5\">3</div>\n<div>Copy the <span class=\"font-mono font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 px-1 border border-blue-200 rounded\">G-XXXX</span> tag</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3 text-xs\">\n<div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-yellow-200 text-yellow-800 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs shrink-0 mt-0.5\">4</div>\n<div>Claude Code: <span class=\"italic text-gray-600\">\"Add this Google Analytics code to header\"</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3 text-xs\">\n<div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-yellow-200 text-yellow-800 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs shrink-0 mt-0.5\">5</div>\n<div>Run <span class=\"font-mono font-bold bg-black text-white px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs\">$ npm run deploy</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3 text-xs\">\n<div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-yellow-200 text-yellow-800 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs shrink-0 mt-0.5\">6</div>\n<div>In GA4, click <strong>\"Test Installation\"</strong> \u2192 Confirm</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Dashboard preview -->\n<div class=\"border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-4 bg-gray-50 relative overflow-hidden\">\n<div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 bg-yellow-400 text-black text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-bl-lg border-b-2 border-l-2 border-black\">GA4 DASHBOARD</div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 text-center mt-2\">\n<div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-200 p-2 rounded shadow-sm\">\n<div class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase\">Users</div>\n<div class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-800\">124</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-200 p-2 rounded shadow-sm\">\n<div class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase\">Realtime</div>\n<div class=\"text-xl font-bold text-blue-600\">12</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-200 p-2 rounded shadow-sm\">\n<div class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase\">Countries</div>\n<div class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-800\">4</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
        "metadata_html": "<div class=\"mb-4\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">Why I saved this:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>Keyword chip design</li><li>Clear conversational structure</li><li>Subtle border styling</li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-6\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">What I can learn:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>Structuring LLM outputs visually</li><li>Tag system UI patterns</li></ul>\n</div>\n<!-- RESTORED: SOURCE METADATA -->\n<div class=\"transparent p-4 rounded border border-white/20 text-sm mt-4 hidden\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-y-2 gap-x-4\">\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Creator:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Tejas Jaware</div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Source:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-[var(--text-primary)]\"><a class=\"underline font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] hover:text-indigo-500\" href=\"paper_micro_tool.html\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">AI Micro-Tools Guide</a></div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Rights:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-gray-500 text-xs italic leading-tight mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Belongs to original creator. Saved for inspiration.</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
