        "visual_html": "<div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden font-sans max-w-full mx-auto\">\n<!-- Browser Header -->\n<div class=\"bg-gray-100 px-4 py-1.5 flex items-center border-b border-gray-200\">\n<div class=\"flex space-x-2 mr-4\">\n<div class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400\"></div>\n<div class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400\"></div>\n<div class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-400\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 flex justify-center\">\n<div class=\"bg-white text-xs text-gray-500 py-1.5 px-4 rounded-md border border-gray-200 max-w-sm w-full flex items-center shadow-inner\">\n<svg class=\"w-3 h-3 mr-2 text-gray-400\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg>\n                instantdomainsearch.com\n            </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Search UI -->\n<div class=\"p-5 bg-gray-50 flex flex-col items-center border-b border-gray-200\">\n<div class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 text-center\">Find the perfect domain name</div>\n<div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl relative\">\n<input class=\"w-full text-base py-1.5 pl-4 pr-12 rounded-full border-2 border-red-500 shadow-sm focus:outline-none bg-white text-gray-800 font-medium\" disabled=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"real online ruler\"/>\n<div class=\"absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-red-500 text-white p-1.5 rounded-full cursor-pointer\">\n<svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Results -->\n<div class=\"p-4 md:p-5 bg-white\">\n<div class=\"w-full flex flex-col gap-2\">\n<!-- Result 1 -->\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-2.5 rounded-lg border-2 border-green-500 bg-green-50 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden\">\n<div class=\"absolute right-0 top-0 bg-green-500 text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-bl-lg uppercase tracking-wider\">Selected Domain</div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col\">\n<div class=\"text-base font-bold text-gray-900 flex items-center m-0\">realonlineruler.com</div>\n<div class=\"text-xs text-green-700 font-medium mt-1\">Exact match, short, easy to spell.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-center text-green-600 font-bold bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded-md border border-green-200 shadow-sm\">\n<svg class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-1\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n                    AVAILABLE\n                </div>\n</div>\n<!-- Result 2 -->\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-col\">\n<div class=\"text-base font-semibold text-gray-400 line-through m-0\">freeonlineruler.com</div>\n<div class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1\">Too long anyway</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-center text-red-500 font-bold bg-red-50 px-2 py-1 rounded-md border border-red-100\">\n<svg class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-1\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n                    TAKEN\n                </div>\n</div>\n<!-- Result 3 -->\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors opacity-75\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-col\">\n<div class=\"text-base font-semibold text-gray-700 m-0\">onlineruler<span class=\"text-orange-500\">.net</span></div>\n<div class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1\">Not preferred (.com is better for trust)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-center text-orange-500 font-bold bg-orange-50 px-2 py-1 rounded-md border border-orange-100\">\n<svg class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-1\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n                    AVOID\n                </div>\n</div>\n<!-- Rules Banner -->\n<div class=\"mt-2 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-3 flex items-start text-xs text-blue-800\">\n<svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mr-2 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg>\n<div class=\"m-0\"><strong>Domain Rules:</strong> Prefer <code>.com</code> for familiarity, try to include the main keyword naturally, and keep it reasonably short.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
        "metadata_html": "<div class=\"mb-4\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">Why I saved this:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>Abstracted UI framing</li><li>Neutral color palette</li><li>Focuses attention on inner content</li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-6\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">What I can learn:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>Using pseudo-browser frames for presentations</li><li>Creating depth with borders</li></ul>\n</div>\n<!-- RESTORED: SOURCE METADATA -->\n<div class=\"transparent p-4 rounded border border-white/20 text-sm mt-4 hidden\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-y-2 gap-x-4\">\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Creator:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Tejas Jaware</div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Source:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-[var(--text-primary)]\"><a class=\"underline font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] hover:text-indigo-500\" href=\"paper_micro_tool.html\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">AI Micro-Tools Guide</a></div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Rights:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-gray-500 text-xs italic leading-tight mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Belongs to original creator. Saved for inspiration.</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
